                    <component type="mcqtawa">
                        <question>
                            <p class="" dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07f7"><![CDATA[If an average size laptop (15.6 inch) has a power consumption of 60 Watts, and is used for 8 hours every day, what would be the monthly (30 days) energy usage?]]></p>
                        </question>
                        <instruction>
                            <component type="instruction">
                                <text dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07f8"><![CDATA[Select one answer, then select 'Submit'.]]></text>
                            </component>
                        </instruction>
                        <submit>
                            <text dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07f9"><![CDATA[Submit]]></text>
                        </submit>
                        <secondary>
                            <text dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07fa"><![CDATA[]]></text>
                        </secondary>
                        <options>
                            <option correct="false">
                                <text dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07fb"><![CDATA[ 1.14 kWh]]></text>
                            </option>
                            <option correct="true">
                                <text dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07fc"><![CDATA[14.4 kWh]]></text>
                            </option>
                            <option correct="false">
                                <text dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07fd"><![CDATA[144.4 kW]]></text>
                            </option>
                        </options>
                    </component>
                    <div class="feedback pb-0 mb-0">
                        <row>
                            <column col_xs="2" col_md="1">
                                <component type="image" svg="tickcross"></component>
                            </column>
                            <column col_xs="10" col_md="11">
                                <component type="text">
                                    <p class="feedbackCorrect feedbackHeading" dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07fe"><![CDATA[That's right.]]></p>
                                    <p class="feedbackIncorrect feedbackHeading" dbid="657ae1eba789759594df07ff"><![CDATA[That's incorrect.]]></p>
                                    <p dbid="6596c74102dd2cb62b72ac86"><![CDATA[ To work out the monthly energy usage, you first need to find out the power consumption, in this case 60 Watts. You then multiply this by the number of hours used a day (8 hours), and then multiply again by the number of days used (30 days). You then divide this figure by 1,000 to get the kWh. ]]></p>
                                    <p dbid="657ae1eba789759594df0800"><![CDATA[60 x 8 = 480]]></p>
                                    <p dbid="657ae1eba789759594df0802"><![CDATA[480 x 30 = 14,400]]></p>
                                    <p dbid="657ae1eba789759594df0803"><![CDATA[14,400 / 1,000 = 14.4 kWh]]></p>
                                </component>
                            </column>
                        </row>
                        <row class="flex-row">
                            <column sm="6" style="
                            align-items: center;
                            justify-items: center;
                            justify-content: start;">
                                <component type="panel" class="bkgColorWhite colorBlack">
                                    <component type="text">
                                        <p>
                                            <b dbid="6596c74102dd2cb62b72ac8a"><![CDATA[ Did you know? ]]></b>
                                        </p>
                                        <p dbid="6596c74102dd2cb62b72ac8b"><![CDATA[14.4 kWh per month generates 13 Lbs of CO2, and is the equivalent of driving 15 miles in a petrol car. (<a href="https://www.perchenergy.com/energy-calculators/computer-power-use-cost#calc" target="_blank">source</a>) ]]></p>
